Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that make \Nyou feel cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaved ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almond jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Polar bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's~ so~ ho~t!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:19.95,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,The color white?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the car's \NGPS showed them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the other side \Nof a tall, tall cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, right next to their ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You should have fallen!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nihihi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Feel colder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too scary, Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh–What do I do, Makoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to \Nsleep alone tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Matterhorn in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A blizzard in Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A blank white schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}that's the coldest it gets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Broken air-conditioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crappy air-conditioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless air-conditioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be repaired the \Nday after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll melt like ice cream and \Nbecome monstrous ooze by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear your heart and soul of worldly \Nthoughts and even fire will become cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought popsicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.24,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ro! Sham! Bo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.11,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I used to live, it was only a little ways to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:40.22,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:40.95,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.35,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.47,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I miss the beautiful sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:44.48,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:45.58,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:46.67,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:47.83,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:48.92,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach! The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it a company trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, I wanna go \Non a company trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D–Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Public welfare and promoting health is part of your job too, Producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as it doesn't \Naffect the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I called around for anyone who didn't have work to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}everyone{\i0\fscx180} {\r}came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true business is slow at the moment, but it's not like we wanted it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would have \Nit tough alone, Producer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fun to go on \Nvacation with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a me~rmaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I baked some cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're \Nhaving fun, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. After all it's \Nthe beach. The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The glimmer of the \Nsun on the waves...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harurun! Trade me for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pay two chocolates from my hand to summon four of Harurun's cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here with all your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takane...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should really look \Ninto getting glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they looked closer, there were \Ncountless handprints on the car window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H–Hey, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though they wiped the prints away, one just wouldn't come off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that one \Nand that one alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was made from the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty meters to destination point!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget your sunscreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like children, getting all worked up over something as dull as the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, leaving everything \Nwhere they tossed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were they really looking \Nforward to the beach that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but being together \Nis what makes it fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The radiance of the summer sun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,frees our hearts to a \Ngreater degree than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it a little disturbing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that not one person has \Nmade a fuss over us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we are an idol agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be so, but only \Nbecause it's still "now".{CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi–ha–ya~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're at the beach, \Nlet's swim together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not a very good swimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun if everyone's there with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take off your t-shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H–Hey, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!{options? CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.28,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.89,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait... Don't push, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets along \Nso well. It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gluttonous silver princess!{options? CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A four, a four-leaf clover–
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Hey, you! You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Pick-up artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "you", it's Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute! Don't you think you could be a celebrity or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I could probably be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You can have that, \Nso come eat something with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, instead of them, come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have these, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have lunch with whoever swims to the other shore fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? All the way over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... Go–!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swim hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a little demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hibiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I got it, ribbit~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Make sure \Nyou have all your things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay–!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He~y! Aren't you \Nforgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, I pretty much expected \Nsomething like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry. There was the budget and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I like how it kind of feels \Nlike a training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It {\i1}is{\i0\fscx110} {\r} a company vacation, \Njust to make that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}First up is the indispensable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Can you peek into the girls' bath?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}check!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, don't run off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming such \Na long distance, and welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good to \Nlie down on tatami{ mats}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's plenty of room even if everyone sleeps here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so calming... {options? CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't very \Nmany channels here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your valuables in here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamuzou is a valuable, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An open-air bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mixed bathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or not. Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone by himself \Nin this tiny room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lonely all by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the loneliest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they get back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is 765 Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chief. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, the project was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's–It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really, really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty more, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U–Um, it's delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Eating outdoors has \Na unique charm, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takane, shall I get \Nsomething for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some corn, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, gimme meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami wants sausage, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget your vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa, go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to put some more \Ncharcoal on, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A–A~h!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A–hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!{options? CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.20,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was for Producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can grill your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather focus on eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H–Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Kotori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, the project was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath is so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should rename the "Large Public Bath" to the "Small Public Bath".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Water Current!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean Splash! {CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we put \Non sunscreen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in \Na good mood, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I forgot the conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next door, next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek...! {CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! {double CHECK!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.36,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.15,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.70,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.37,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:50.24,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:50.59,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.61,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.15,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:51.55,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:51.95,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:52.37,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:52.82,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:53.18,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:53.48,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.96,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have left my \Ncell phone on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I need to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you keep \Ntelling scary stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get back, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told you the end to that story about the beach at night, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W–Wait, now's \Nnot really the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was so late, there was a \Nwoman swimming just past the breakwaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than swimming, it was \Nmore like she was just floating there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When their eyes met, \Nthe woman came ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her pale white skin... \Nher long white hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they looked into her face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Takane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't just stand there \Nwatching the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hibiki, you lack elegance. {options? CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Look. This moon is not something one could see so easily in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're right. So pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels nice, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, do you not like going \Non trips with everyone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the reason singing jobs don't come my way is that I lack ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, lessons are more \Nimportant than having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like quietly listening to the \Nsound of the waves like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many is that, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares how many!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you too, Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a minor, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, all for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:48.42,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to sing, Miura Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, despite the events that led to us coming here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were able to deepen the \Nbonds between everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it turned out for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not going to stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts... scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients for rice balls are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...strawberry bavarois...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking to each other...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt kind of like a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be great if we \Ncould come next year, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think \Nwe'll be like next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd probably be something like, more \Nand more work building up for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! I'd be so happy if we had our own weekly shows or something.{she doesn't say TV shows, but that's probably what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing more concerts, \Nputting out more CD's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe one of us would \Neven be Top Idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, wearing a stage costume with lots of lace and frills...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you all carefree. {options? CHECK}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at reality for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring Ritsuko for the moment, \Njust look at that unreliable Producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about relying on him, \NI wonder if he can keep his job here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? It looks like he's \Nworking really diligently to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, didn't he show up at a meeting recently with bed hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it's because \Nwe have that kind of Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the rest of us need \Nto look out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we do, then I just know even the things Haruka was just talking about–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that really happened
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we wouldn't be able to go on trips like this together any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thing about those things \N{\i1}after{\i0\fscx210} {\r}you've achieved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air conditioner is fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The repairs just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are finally comfortable around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with our batteries \Ncharged, it's time to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'd like to get back to \Nlessons right now, if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki, you're so tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamuzou is, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shijou, you didn't tan at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything comes \Ndown to discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Let's go over our \Nschedule for after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have rested up some \Nwhile I was running around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M–My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, these are souvenirs from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! Well, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:22:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your plan regarding the formation \Nof the new unit, Ryuuguu Komachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been officially approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuguu Komachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next week, \Non iDOLM@STER!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Here's a surprise quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Who's talking right now? \NIs it Ami? Is it Mami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I bet you're totally on the edge \Nof your seat to know who
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}so check next week \Nfor the correct answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Look forward to it!
